article_title: Clawson delivers tea party's State of the Union rebuttal
article_text: - Rep. Curt Clawson (R-Fla.) delivered the tea party's response to President Obama's State of the Union address on Tuesday, saying Obama's plan to raise taxes "is wrong" and "we can do better" than Obamacare. ()
